Working with Integrity.

We're ready when you are.

Life insurance can be tricky

We don’t think it needs to be – which is exactly why we created Integrity. Our business is all about making life insurance simpler, easier and more accessible, so you can get on with doing what you do best - helping your clients.

Why Integrity?

Determined to be different (and better), we co-created Integrity with the help of advisers to build a business that is here to support your customers. We are here now and will consider all new business and review opportunities.

Real opportunities, real partners

We want you to think of us as an extra pair of (skilled) hands, and an extension of your business. With us you can expect

  • A true partnership, we are dedicated to supporting you through policy design, administration and claims allowing you to focus on your core proposition, advice.
  • A CPD accredited group risk insurance training program to enhance your skills or introduce a new revenue source into your business.
  • Great pricing.
  • Responsive and accessible with fast turnaround times.
  • A knowledgeable team who can give you the support you need.
  • Fair outcomes and decisions for your customers.
  • Optional executive policy with no waiting periods on specified injuries, additional lump sum payments for specified crisis events and nursing care benefits during the waiting period.
  • Clear, proactive communication so you’re never kept guessing.
  • Meticulous data management, so you only have to provide information once.

Financial Services Council Membership
We are a full member of the Financial Services Council and subscribe to the Life Insurance Code of Practice which establishes mandatory customer service standards for the life insurance industry. The Code can be found on the FSC website.

Chris Powell

Managing Director and CEO

Integrity is led by Chris Powell, former CFO of Zurich Insurance Group, Australia and New Zealand. He has held several senior leadership roles in Australian financial services businesses including NRMA, State Super Corporation, CBA and Centric Wealth to name a few. Chris truly believes that customer- centricity is the future and together with his highly experienced team, is interrogating all areas of life insurance in order to offer life insurance for people, helping them when they need help most.
